{"tid":1992955,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［有冇HKTV人知點解］有少少覺得自己係condom","createTime":"2020-04-28T12:30:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T03:20:42.000Z","uid":172626,"like":9,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"3a84c4ebd6ca2267739c81821fb1e502e6533360","tid":1992955,"uid":172626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T12:30:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u0j3ATp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu0j3ATp.png&h=c0edc8c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c3Z7h6v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc3Z7h6v.jpg&h=3d8816f2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申返我係好小做大公司，純粹係覺得HKTV係黃先去試下<br />\n<br />\n是咁的，事源係幾日前大部分既HKTVmall PT都收到一個通知，內容大致係公司規矩例行要同PT 轉一次合約，所以要有一個<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為期1-2個月嘅過渡期</span></span>，咁我就問下啲做得長既PT 啦，佢地都話每年係會定一日同PT轉合約既，但係唔會要停咁耐，而且佢又唔講原因比我哋知點解要停咁耐。<br />\n<br />\n但奇怪在佢<span style=\"color: red;\">同一時間請咗好多新既PT 返嚟</span>，我地好多PT都係因為知佢係黃店，我地辭左工，再轉入黎HKTVMALL 做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我地而家好多PT 都係返咗幾個月就比人停工，而家市道又咁樣好難揾PT<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實我地係唔係比人用<span style=\"color: red;\">軟性被迫辭工</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/22.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔想比人當condom呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有啲人又話可以係因為爆咗418 所以就比人炒。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有冇HKTVmall 既員工知道內情 or 有收到風點解公司會要PT 停咁耐工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89a897f39f0641b76c7a769ed81f98612fc7720f","tid":1992955,"uid":172626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-28T12:33:00.000Z","msg":"其實係單一個區有呢個情況定係全部區既PT都要等成個幾兩個月<img src=\"/assets/fac